**To authorize Client VPN ingress**

The following ``authorize-client-vpn-ingress`` example adds an authorization rule for all groups to access the specified network. ::

    aws ec2 authorize-client-vpn-ingress \
        --client-vpn-endpoint-id cvpn-endpoint-123456789123abcde \
        --target-network-cidr 10.0.0.0/16 \
        --authorize-all-groups

Output::

    {
        "Status": {
            "Code": "authorizing"
        }
    }
